<br>
NBG is an amorphous concept and different people have different ideas what it means.  If we are assuming a relatively efficient economy, an item won by the group should roughly provide the same upgrade potential for each group member.  Random loot rules seem to me to be a very fair way of allocating loot.<br>
<br>
NBG, in pick-up groups, often tends to award the most vocal (in some cases selfish) group members.  I definitely agree that it should be random in pick-up groups.<br>
<br>
